[[File:CircutCider.png|thumb|Three containers, one of which contains circuit cider.]]
'''Circuit cider''' was the name of a popular drink that could be found at [[Doodnik's Café]], on the [[Mining/Legends|mining]] [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Tyne's Horky]].<ref name="The Lost Prince">{{DroidsCite|The Lost Prince}}</ref> Although it was one of [[Doodnik Sharpelz]]'s signature drinks, it was also served at [[Dex's Diner/Legends|Dex's Diner]], which was located in [[CoCo Town/Legends|CoCo Town]], [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Authentic circuit cider was made by filtering the liquid through spare [[Droid/Legends|droid]] parts. At Dex's Diner, it was made with parts repurposed from a [[Dishwasher/Legends|dishwasher]] unit that was no longer in service after the waitress droid [[WA-7 waitress droid|WA-7]] learned it had gossipped about her with other appliances. Dex's Diner charged 2.7 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] for the beverage.<ref name="Dex's Diner">{{Hyperspace|url=fans/hyperspace/source/dexdiner/index.html|text=Dining at Dex's|int=Dining at Dex's}}</ref>

